[604.521467, "i", "cat /app/run/README.txt\n"]
[604.522882, "o", "cat /app/run/README.txt\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[604.52357, "o", "Runtime state files for the simulator. The built driver is installed to /usr/local/bin/arena.\r\n\r\n## CLI\r\n\r\n```\r\narena --scenario <basic|stress|stress2> --profile <burst|steady> --order <a_then_b|b_then_a> --out <path> [--seed <n>]\r\n```\r\n\r\nLoad profiles fire on every tick for the full scenario length, including ticks while the client is detached. Detach stops notification handoff to the live client, not submission ingestion.\r\n\r\nDetach writes a journal stamp (u32 generation, u64 cursor — 12 bytes per stamp). The stress2 scenario performs two detach cycles.\r\n\r\n## Report JSON\r\n\r\nPath: `/app/output/report.json`\r\n\r\nTop-level keys: `scenario` (string), `profile` (string), `events` (array).\r\n\r\nEach event object has `kind` (`submit`, `complete`, or `notify`) and `id` (integer request id).\r\n"]
[604.523937, "o", "\u001b[?2004h"]
[604.524027, "o", "root@11b6bf757a9f:/app# "]
[650.194244, "i", "make clean -C /app && make -C /app 2>&1\n"]
[650.19496, "o", "make clean -C /app && make -C /app 2>&1\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[650.197655, "o", "make: Entering directory '/app'\r\nrm -f /usr/local/bin/arena\r\n"]
[650.198431, "o", "make: Leaving directory '/app'\r\n"]
[650.20028, "o", "make: Entering directory '/app'\r\nmkdir -p /usr/local/bin\r\n"]
[650.201064, "o", "cc -O2 -g -std=c11 -Wall -Wextra -Wshadow -Wconversion -Iinclude -o /usr/local/bin/arena src/main.c src/cli.c src/tb_err.c src/report.c src/runtime/runtime.c src/runtime/profile.c src/runtime/script.c src/core/idgen.c src/core/queue.c src/core/map_u64.c src/core/vec_u64.c src/core/vec_ev.c src/io/fs.c src/io/journal.c src/logic/ingest.c src/logic/settle.c src/logic/nudge.c src/logic/merge.c src/logic/link.c \r\n"]
[650.763311, "o", "make: Leaving directory '/app'\r\n"]
